- And I'm proud o' what I done. - we sentence...

429
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:54,750
埃里克·拉马斯内尔...
Ellic Lemasniel...

430
00:33:54,780 --> 00:33:56,350
我没什么好遗憾的了
I'm proud o' what I done.

431
00:33:56,380 --> 00:33:58,280
- 囚禁于... - 我问心无愧!
- to incarceration... - I took a stand!

432
00:33:58,320 --> 00:33:59,550
本密室深处岩床中
in the bedrock beneath this chamber.

433
00:34:01,360 --> 00:34:02,890
