Arise, Sentinel,

434
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:06,390
将这个犯人送进监牢
and carry the condemned to prison.

435
00:34:17,170 --> 00:34:19,640
你将被永囚于黑暗
You'll never see daylight again.

436
00:34:23,610 --> 00:34:27,180
不 不! 你也许能困住我
No, no! You may hold me now,

437
00:34:27,210 --> 00:34:30,120
但你困不住我们所有人!
but you'll never have us all!

438
00:34:42,660 --> 00:34:44,600
这是什么?
What is that?

439
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:52,540
嘿 孩子
Hey, kid.

440
00:34:52,570 --> 00:34:54,540
你要做什么?
What are you doing?

441
00:35:04,890 --> 00:35:07,220
你好 神父
Hello, Father.

442
00:35:17,230 --> 00:35:18,360
挺住啊 老伙计
Still with us, old friend.

443
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,870
他还活着?
He's alive?

444
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:21,870
快不行了
Barely.

445
00:35:21,900 --> 00:35:23,400
他被诅咒了
He's been cursed.

446
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:25,540
怎么会?
How?

447
00:35:25,570 --> 00:35:26,910
蝇马利
Musca Mali.

448
00:35:26,940 --> 00:35:28,210
瘟疫蝇
Plague fly.

449
00:35:28,240 --> 00:35:30,480
13世纪的黑魔法
13th-century black magic.

450
00:35:30,510 --> 00:35:32,240
源自黑巫后之树 对吧?
They were created in the tree of the Queen, correct?

451
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:34,480
是的
That's right.

452
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:36,550
