is to kill the witch who cast it.

463
00:36:01,610 --> 00:36:03,540
那个埃里克效命的人
The one Ellic works for.

464
00:36:04,910 --> 00:36:08,110
多兰最多只能撑两天
Dolan's got two days, tops.

465
00:36:08,150 --> 00:36:10,350
为了我 坚持住
Hang in there, for me.

466
00:36:26,530 --> 00:36:28,470
死亡
Death.

467
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:31,270
那是多兰留的消息 不是凶手留的
It's a message from Dolan, not the killer.

468
00:36:37,180 --> 00:36:38,650
"回忆你的死亡"
"Remember your death."

469
00:36:38,680 --> 00:36:40,680
什么意思?
What does it mean?

470
00:36:42,720 --> 00:36:45,720
唯一能让我回想起自己的死亡的...
There's only one way to remember my death...

471
00:36:45,750 --> 00:36:47,650
只有魔法
Magic.

472
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:53,690
