and puts it in a sack on his belt.

484
00:37:44,980 --> 00:37:45,950
拜托! 这只是保姆讲给孩子们听
C'mon! That's just a story nannies tell children

485
00:37:45,980 --> 00:37:47,210
吓唬他们的
so they behave.

486
00:37:47,250 --> 00:37:50,750
克洛伊 快走吧
Chloe, you need to leave.

487
00:37:50,780 --> 00:37:53,850
米兰达 米兰达!
Miranda. Miranda!

488
00:38:00,130 --> 00:38:03,300
我们守规矩的 这里没有人类
We're up to code. There are no humans here.

489
00:38:03,330 --> 00:38:05,360
地方不错啊
Beautiful place.

490
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:07,230
谢谢
Thank you.

491
00:38:07,270 --> 00:38:09,870
