Now, what in the world would you be afraid of?

507
00:38:52,450 --> 00:38:54,810
演讲
Public speaking.

508
00:38:54,850 --> 00:38:55,950
你知道我怕什么吗?
You know what I'm afraid of?

509
00:38:55,980 --> 00:38:57,450
说吧
Enlighten me.

510
