And I also know that I haven't done anything wrong,

513
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:15,130
所以除非你准备一枪打爆我 不然的话 恕不远送
so unless you're gonna put a gun to my head, get out.

514
00:39:15,170 --> 00:39:19,040
你没说错 我是讲规矩的
You know, you're right. I do have a code.

515
00:39:19,070 --> 00:39:23,280
