To help an old friend.

519
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:47,970
事先提醒
But a word of warning to you.

520
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,070
如果在记忆中受伤
If you get injured in your memory,

521
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:51,300
