What did you want me to see?

532
00:42:49,550 --> 00:42:52,450
卡尔德!
Kaulder!

533
00:42:52,490 --> 00:42:54,620
卡尔德
Kaulder.

534
00:42:57,390 --> 00:43:00,060
卡尔德 醒醒
Kaulder, wake up.

535
00:43:12,570 --> 00:43:15,210
你好啊 巫师猎人
Well, hello, witch hunter.

536
00:43:18,510 --> 00:43:21,580
