I was yanked out of a memory spell once.

537
00:43:21,610 --> 00:43:24,050
脑子迷糊了好几个小时
My mind was scrambled eggs for hours.

538
00:43:27,650 --> 00:43:30,260
要知道 人类不该去寻找过去
You know, people shouldn't root around in their past.

539
00:43:30,290 --> 00:43:32,990
有些事情 还是忘记比较好
Some things are best left forgotten.

540
00:43:54,480 --> 00:43:56,420
