Doesn't take much balls to get in a bar fight

545
00:44:49,570 --> 00:44:51,500
都不用先壮胆了吧
when you can't get hurt.

546
00:44:57,240 --> 00:44:58,540
可惜你的思维没有...
Too bad your mind isn't as tough

547
00:44:58,580 --> 00:45:00,510
你身体这么强壮
as the rest of you.

548
00:45:01,580 --> 00:45:03,220
不会有酒吧了
No more bar.

549
00:45:03,250 --> 00:45:05,790
也不会有记忆药水了
No more memory potions for you.

550
00:45:53,630 --> 00:45:55,570
呼吸啊
Breathe.

551
00:45:56,670 --> 00:45:57,700
呼吸啊
Breathe.

552
