800年了 你的气数也该用尽了
After 800 years, you've run out of time.

553
00:46:22,460 --> 00:46:25,300
死期将至 巫师猎人!
Death is coming, witch hunter!

554
00:46:40,980 --> 00:46:43,280
你和别人说的恶魔没两样
You are the monster they say you are.

555
00:46:44,520 --> 00:46:47,150
都怪你! 这是我全部家当了!
Damn you! This place was all I had!

556
00:49:13,700 --> 00:49:14,830
克洛伊!
Chloe!

557
00:49:14,870 --> 00:49:16,800
抓住我的手!
Grab my hand!

558
00:49:35,590 --> 00:49:37,590
地方不错啊
Nice view.

559
00:49:54,540 --> 00:49:57,540
坚持住 孩子
Just hold on, kid.

560
00:49:57,580 --> 00:50:00,780
我发誓 我会找出凶手 破除诅咒
I promise I'll find who did this and break the curse.

561
00:50:00,810 --> 00:50:02,450
卡尔德! 看这个!
Kaulder! Come see this!

562
00:50:02,480 --> 00:50:05,020
我接入联邦调查局数据库了
I've got the FBI database online.

563
00:50:12,490 --> 00:50:13,530
等等 倒回去
Stop, go back one.

564
00:50:13,560 --> 00:50:14,560
继续
Continuing.

565
00:50:14,590 --> 00:50:16,500
不是 不是他
No, not him.

566
00:50:16,530 --> 00:50:17,630
停下
Stop.

567
00:50:17,660 --> 00:50:19,970
就是他
That's him.

568
00:50:20,000 --> 00:50:22,830
为什么他不想我回忆起自己的死?
But why doesn't he want me to remember my death?

569
00:50:22,870 --> 00:50:25,400
姓名 巴尔塔萨·凯托拉
Born Baltasar Ketola.

570
00:50:25,440 --> 00:50:27,010
又名贝利亚 芬兰国籍
Goes by Belial. Finnish national.

571
00:50:27,040 --> 00:50:29,840
他就是埃里克卖命的主子
He's the one Ellic was working for.

572
00:50:29,880 --> 00:50:32,940
就是他诅咒了多兰?
The one who cursed Dolan?

573
00:50:32,980 --> 00:50:34,450
为了毁灭这世界
Every generation has to be given

574
00:50:34,480 --> 00:50:36,650
巫师还真是一代代不死不休啊
their chance to destroy the world.

575
00:50:36,680 --> 00:50:39,190
但我们大部分人和他不同
Yet most of us aren't like him, you know.

576
00:50:39,220 --> 00:50:42,050
我们和你们差不多
We're the same as you.

577
00:50:42,090 --> 00:50:45,420
你的外貌也许和我们相似 内里却不同
You may look like us, but you're not.

578
00:50:45,460 --> 00:50:47,730
你血液中流淌着魔法
You've got magic in your blood.

579
00:50:47,760 --> 00:50:50,060
足以酿成大祸的魔法
Magic that can do very bad things.

580
00:50:50,100 --> 00:50:51,730
之前在你酒吧 我们被打断了
We were interrupted back in your bar.

581
00:50:51,760 --> 00:50:53,530
- 哦 是哦 - 我必须再试一次
- Oh, yes. - I have to try again.

582
00:50:53,570 --> 00:50:55,800
是哦 我的酒吧!
Yes, my bar!

583
00:50:55,840 --> 00:50:59,540
我在乎的所有东西都付诸一炬了
Where everything I cared about burnt to the ground.

584
00:50:59,570 --> 00:51:01,870
但我不是在怪你毁了我的生活
But I'm not blaming you for destroying

585
00:51:01,910 --> 00:51:04,040
或是其他什么东西
my life or anything.

586
00:51:04,080 --> 00:51:07,010
我恨的是自己只能冷眼旁观
I'm just making an observation.

587
00:51:07,050 --> 00:51:11,550
看着你怎么毁掉我的一切
An observation on how you destroyed my life.

588
00:51:12,750 --> 00:51:14,120
我走了
I'm leaving.

589
00:51:14,150 --> 00:51:17,760
听着 我也不想事情变成这样
Look, I don't like it any more than you do,

590
00:51:17,790 --> 00:51:21,830
但如果你帮助我 我会保证你的人身安全
but if you help me, I promise to keep you safe.

591
00:51:26,770 --> 00:51:28,130
我需要雪墩山柳菊
I'll need more Snowdonia hawkweed

592
00:51:28,170 --> 00:51:30,240
配新的记忆药水
to mix another memory potion.

593
00:51:30,270 --> 00:51:31,700
我手下一个姑娘米兰达
Miranda, the girl who works for me,

594
00:51:31,740 --> 00:51:32,940
有一大批存货
has a pretty good stash.

595
00:51:32,970 --> 00:51:34,010
我短信她
Um, I'll text her.

596
00:51:34,040 --> 00:51:35,980
谢谢
Thank you.

597
00:51:37,710 --> 00:51:40,510
贝利亚的夹克上有红色的土
Belial had red soil on his jacket.

598
00:51:40,550 --> 00:51:41,880
红土?
Red soil?

599
00:51:41,920 --> 00:51:44,550
分析一下 看看有什么结果
Analyze this and see what we get.

600
00:51:44,580 --> 00:51:45,750
好的
Of course.

601
00:51:50,020 --> 00:51:51,960
是米兰达
It's Miranda.

602
00:51:53,660 --> 00:51:55,790
她喜欢猫
She's a cat person.

603
00:51:55,830 --> 00:51:58,130
嗨! 嗨
Hey! Hey, there.

604
00:51:58,160 --> 00:52:00,600
没有 我还活着
No, I'm not dead yet.

605
00:52:00,630 --> 00:52:01,870
好了 等她来了
Right, so when she gets here,

606
00:52:01,900 --> 00:52:04,540
不要乱动啊 好吗?
don't make any sudden moves, okay?

607
00:52:04,570 --> 00:52:06,740
别和她眼神接触
Don't make eye contact.

608
00:52:06,770 --> 00:52:08,610
也不要说话
Or talk.

609
00:52:08,640 --> 00:52:10,880
哇哦
Whoa.

610
00:52:11,910 --> 00:52:13,850
抱歉
Sorry.

611
00:52:26,230 --> 00:52:28,160
就是这个了
This is it here.

612
00:52:31,630 --> 00:52:33,230
不行 这个还没发芽呢
No, it hasn't sprouted yet.

613
00:52:33,270 --> 00:52:34,700
你到底加了多少
How many witch hunter

614
00:52:34,730 --> 00:52:36,940
巫师猎人交流群?
discussion groups are you a part of?

615
00:52:36,970 --> 00:52:40,540
"永生的屠杀狂魔法西斯..."
"Genocidal immortal fascist..."

616
00:52:43,080 --> 00:52:45,210
你们巫师是这么形容我的吗?
So that's what you witches think of me, huh?

617
00:52:45,240 --> 00:52:48,250
那人类又是怎么形容我们的呢?
What is it that people know about us, anyway?

618
00:52:48,280 --> 00:52:50,680
绿皮肤
That we have green skin

619
00:52:50,720 --> 00:52:51,750
戴着尖顶帽
and like to wear pointy hats,

620
00:52:51,780 --> 00:52:53,050
脾气暴躁
and that we're mean

621
00:52:53,090 --> 00:52:55,920
被烧死在塞勒姆的火刑柱上?
and got burned at the stake in Salem?

622
00:52:58,990 --> 00:53:01,590
塞勒姆小镇的事是错的
Salem was wrong,

623
00:53:01,630 --> 00:53:04,200
那些女人是无辜的
And those women innocent.

624
00:53:04,230 --> 00:53:07,330
如果那些女人真的是巫师呢?
But what if those women really were witches?

625
00:53:07,370 --> 00:53:09,730
她们就活该被烧死吗?
Would it then have been okay?

626
00:53:09,770 --> 00:53:14,110
我记得自己想过 如果是我被判刑的话
See, I remember thinking if it was me found guilty,

627
00:53:15,610 --> 00:53:17,810
没人会在乎
no one would care.

628
00:53:17,840 --> 00:53:19,780
我在乎
I would.

629
00:53:28,710 --> 00:53:30,910
山柳菊没了 它不见了
The hawkweed's gone. It's gone.

630
00:53:30,940 --> 00:53:33,080
有人把它拿走了 它不在这了
I mean, someone's taken it. It's not here.

631
00:53:35,410 --> 00:53:37,350
卡尔德?
Kaulder?

632
00:53:38,380 --> 00:53:40,550
怎么了?
What?

633
00:53:40,590 --> 00:53:43,450
- 怎么了? - 别看
- What? - No.

634
00:53:43,490 --> 00:53:45,390
是米兰达
Miranda.

635
00:53:45,430 --> 00:53:46,960
米兰达!
Miranda!

636
00:53:54,400 --> 00:53:57,040
你来晚了 巫师猎人
You're too late, witch hunter.

637
00:53:57,070 --> 00:54:00,710
她死的真惨 既恐惧
She died badly, screaming.

638
00:54:00,740 --> 00:54:03,210
又孤单
Alone.

639
00:54:03,240 --> 00:54:05,210
就和你将来的下场一样
Just like you will.

640
00:54:18,460 --> 00:54:20,930
你会抓到凶手的 对吗?
You're gonna get who did this, right?

641
00:54:21,060 --> 00:54:24,000
我会解决贝利亚的
I'll handle Belial.

642
00:54:24,030 --> 00:54:26,300
很好
Good.

643
00:54:28,140 --> 00:54:31,210
我不知道还有哪里能弄到所需的材料
I don't know where else to get the stuff that we need.

644
00:54:33,550 --> 00:54:35,680
有一个地方
There is one place.

645
00:54:38,580 --> 00:54:42,550
不过那里充斥着旧货币 古魔法 非常危险
But it's old money, old magic, and dangerous.

646
00:54:55,940 --> 00:54:57,870
抱歉
I'm sorry.

647
00:55:17,960 --> 00:55:18,920
卡尔德?
Kaulder?

648
00:55:18,960 --> 00:55:20,890
索尼娅
Sonya.

649
00:55:25,360 --> 00:55:27,300
丹妮卡可是个大忙人
Danique's been so busy,

650
00:55:27,330 --> 00:55:28,870
我很讶异她竟会同意见你
I'm surprised that she agreed to see you.

651
00:55:28,900 --> 00:55:29,870
我想她不会喜欢
I don't think she would have liked

652
00:55:29,900 --> 00:55:31,370
另一个选择的后果
the alternative.

653
00:55:48,920 --> 00:55:51,420
卡尔德先生 很高兴你今晚能来
Mr. Kaulder, you've made my night.

654
00:55:53,230 --> 00:55:55,190
请坐
Please have a seat.

655
00:55:56,760 --> 00:55:58,960
你是从哪里捡来这个小朋友的 二手商店?
Where'd you rescue your little friend from, a thrift shop?

656
00:55:59,000 --> 00:55:59,960
小朋友...
Little friend....

657
00:56:03,740 --> 00:56:06,470
告诉我 什么事那么急?
So tell me, what is this emergency?

658
00:56:06,510 --> 00:56:07,910
你有什么必须要想起来的?
What is it you just must remember?

659
00:56:07,940 --> 00:56:11,210
他丢了他的车钥匙
He lost his car keys.

660
00:56:11,240 --> 00:56:12,910
我要给你多少钱?
How much do I owe you?

661
00:56:12,950 --> 00:56:15,250
一分钱也不用 只要你陪我喝一杯就好
Oh, nothing. You have a drink with me. That's my price.

662
00:56:15,280 --> 00:56:17,380
你知道我为何而来
You know what I'm here for.

663
00:56:20,720 --> 00:56:23,990
芸芸众生都试图伪装自己
So many of us pretend to be something that we're not.

664
00:56:24,020 --> 00:56:28,360
可是你 却真实的活着
But you, you've lived.

665
00:56:28,390 --> 00:56:30,760
你穿越了历史的长河
A man who's walked through history.

666
00:56:30,800 --> 00:56:34,370
你见过拿破仑 斯大林
To have known Napoleon, Stalin,

667
00:56:34,400 --> 00:56:36,300
希特勒...
Hitler...

668
00:56:36,340 --> 00:56:40,240
别怀旧了 这个时代已经够邪恶了
No need to be nostalgic. We have enough evil now.

669
00:56:40,270 --> 00:56:43,440
他们和你没有太大的不同
They're not so different than you.

670
00:56:43,480 --> 00:56:45,880
他们用自己的力量来改变世界
They used their power to change the world.

671
00:56:45,910 --> 00:56:48,550
你不能改变过去所做之事
You can't change what you've done.

672
00:56:52,620 --> 00:56:55,490
卡尔德! 这株植物有点不对劲
Kaulder! There's something wrong with this plant.

673
00:57:02,300 --> 00:57:03,260
你来了
You're here.

674
00:57:03,300 --> 00:57:05,230
卡尔德...
Kaulder...

675
00:57:07,470 --> 00:57:09,530
卡尔德! 卡尔德!
Kaulder! Kaulder!

676
00:57:09,570 --> 00:57:11,500
- 欢迎来到天堂 - 卡尔德!
- Enjoy paradise. - Kaulder!

677
00:57:11,540 --> 00:57:13,470
卡尔德 那些烟 别...
Kaulder, it's smoke. Don't...

678
00:57:20,350 --> 00:57:22,310
看 父亲 看!
Look, Daddy. Look!

679
00:57:22,350 --> 00:57:24,280
它们要飞到南方过冬了
They're flying south for the winter.

680
00:57:30,060 --> 00:57:33,290
卡尔德 听我说
Kaulder, listen to me.

681
00:57:33,330 --> 00:57:36,560
你中了陷阱 我需要你醒来
You are in a trap and I need you to wake up.

682
00:57:45,770 --> 00:57:48,810
你在这里是找不到答案的
You're not gonna find any answers here.

683
00:57:48,840 --> 00:57:51,540
呆的时间越长 你就越难离开
The longer you wait, the harder it is to get out.

684
00:58:00,550 --> 00:58:02,590
卡尔德 卡尔德
Kaulder. Kaulder.

685
00:58:02,620 --> 00:58:05,620
我需要你醒来 这一切都不是真实的
I need you to wake up. None of this is real.

686
00:58:05,660 --> 00:58:07,690
卡尔德 你中计了!
Kaulder, you are in a trap!

687
00:58:13,000 --> 00:58:14,930
快回来
Come back.

688
00:58:17,100 --> 00:58:19,400
卡尔德 如果你不马上醒来
Kaulder, if you don't wake up right now,

689
00:58:19,440 --> 00:58:22,070
我们都会死的!
we are both going to die!

690
00:58:22,110 --> 00:58:24,110
快醒醒!
Wake up!

691
00:58:24,140 --> 00:58:26,080
克洛伊...
Chloe...

692
00:58:32,420 --> 00:58:35,820
这不是真的
This isn't real.

693
00:58:35,860 --> 00:58:39,560
卡尔德! 快醒醒!
Kaulder! Wake up!

694
00:58:40,990 --> 00:58:42,460
把车开到巷子里
Pull the car into the alley

695
00:58:42,490 --> 00:58:43,930
然后把他扔进后备箱
and throw him in the trunk.

696
00:58:43,960 --> 00:58:45,800
我们将因为打败巫师猎人
We're going down in history

697
00:58:45,830 --> 00:58:47,830
而闻名于世了
as the ones who beat the witch hunter.

698
00:58:52,970 --> 00:58:54,570
拜托
Come on.

699
00:58:54,610 --> 00:58:56,540
出去
Get out.

700
00:59:05,020 --> 00:59:07,390
葬土
Burial dirt.

701
00:59:07,420 --> 00:59:10,360
是黑暗魔法最强大的原料
Nothing more powerful for dark magic.

702
00:59:14,130 --> 00:59:16,460
贝利亚要用它来做什么?
What does Belial want with it?

703
00:59:16,490 --> 00:59:18,500
谁?
Who?

704
00:59:19,760 --> 00:59:22,100
"回忆我的死亡"
"Remember my death."

705
00:59:22,130 --> 00:59:25,370
他到底不想让我知道什么?
What is it that he doesn't want me to see?

706
00:59:26,910 --> 00:59:30,010
住手! 拜托了
Stop! Please.

707
00:59:32,710 --> 00:59:34,680
贝利亚什么也没告诉我
Belial didn't tell me anything.

708
00:59:34,710 --> 00:59:36,850
我只负责帮他弄到土
I helped him get the dirt.

709
00:59:36,880 --> 00:59:38,980
我自己私藏了一丁点
I just took a little bit for myself.

710
00:59:39,020 --> 00:59:41,950
可他有一大堆
He has tons of it.

711
00:59:41,990 --> 00:59:43,920
拜托了?
Please?

712
00:59:50,960 --> 00:59:53,060
谢谢你的酒
Thanks for the drink.

713
00:59:55,800 --> 00:59:58,440
你这个巫师族的叛徒!
You are a traitor to your kind!

714
00:59:59,900 --> 01:00:02,510
你知道我为什么喜欢旧货商店吗?
You know what I like about thrift shops?

715
01:00:03,840 --> 01:00:05,980
因为那里的一切都是老的
Everything in them is old.

716
01:00:30,000 --> 01:00:32,100
贱人
Bitch.

717
01:00:41,250 --> 01:00:43,450
现在你知道了
So now you know.

718
01:00:47,890 --> 01:00:50,550
你是一个梦行者
You're a dream-walker.

719
01:00:50,590 --> 01:00:53,560
人人都知道梦行是一种黑暗的天赋
Everyone knows that dream-walking is a black gift.

720
01:00:56,530 --> 01:01:00,600
我一辈子都在试图隐藏它
I've spent my entire life trying to hide from it.

721
01:01:00,630 --> 01:01:03,840
你知道我会发现你的秘密 可你并不在乎
You knew I would discover your secret, and you didn't care.

722
01:01:05,840 --> 01:01:08,140
你还是义无反顾地将我拉出陷阱
You still pulled me out of that trap.

723
01:01:09,170 --> 01:01:12,180
那真是非常勇敢的举动
It was a very brave thing to do.

724
01:01:12,210 --> 01:01:15,150
我有东西要给你看 来吧
Let me show you something. Come on.

725
01:01:16,250 --> 01:01:18,480
晚安 麦克斯!
Good night, Max!

726
01:01:46,080 --> 01:01:48,280
你是我族的耻辱
You are a disgrace to our kind.

727
01:01:48,310 --> 01:01:50,710
贝利亚 我别无选择
Belial, I had no choice.

728
01:01:50,750 --> 01:01:52,880
卡尔德威胁说要把我活活打死
Kaulder threatened to beat me to death with his bare hands.

729
01:01:52,920 --> 01:01:55,020
我们会处置你的 叛徒
We have plans for you, traitor.

730
01:01:56,860 --> 01:01:57,890
你得理解我 贝利亚
You must understand, Belial.

731
01:02:01,060 --> 01:02:02,790
好好享受那些影子吧
Enjoy the shadows.

732
01:02:24,780 --> 01:02:29,320
这是巫师的历史 你们的历史
This is the history of witches. Your history.

733
01:02:31,160 --> 01:02:32,320
那是你
That's you.

734
01:02:32,360 --> 01:02:33,790
对
Yeah.

735
01:02:33,830 --> 01:02:36,190
至少眼睛很形象
Least they got your eyes right.

736
01:02:38,400 --> 01:02:40,830
这些都是梦行者
These are the dream-walkers.

737
01:02:40,870 --> 01:02:43,340
黑巫后身边最致命的刺客
The Witch Queen's deadliest assassins.

738
01:02:43,370 --> 01:02:45,170
他们会用某种方式进入你的脑中
Somehow they used to jump into your mind

739
01:02:45,200 --> 01:02:47,810
窥探你最珍贵的记忆
and pry out your most precious memories.

740
01:02:47,840 --> 01:02:51,980
并把它们转化成你最可怕的噩梦
And then they'd twist 'em into your worst nightmares.

741
01:02:52,010 --> 01:02:53,240
你是在给我上历史课
What, you're giving a history lesson here

742
01:02:53,280 --> 01:02:55,080
还是只为了吓我?
or you're just trying to scare me?

743
01:02:55,110 --> 01:02:57,750
关于梦行者 有一件事无人知晓
There's something no one knows about dream-walkers.

744
01:02:59,020 --> 01:03:02,020
他们不需要什么记忆药水
They don't need memory potions.

745
01:03:02,050 --> 01:03:05,220
那种力量是他们与生俱来的
That power lies within them.

746
01:03:05,260 --> 01:03:07,790
我的脑海深处有一样
I have something buried deep in my mind

747
01:03:07,830 --> 01:03:09,900
必须回想起来的事
that I must remember.

748
01:03:11,800 --> 01:03:14,870
你是唯一一个能帮助我找回记忆的人
And you're the only one that can help me.

749
01:03:14,900 --> 01:03:16,130
不 我不行
No, I can't.

750
01:03:16,170 --> 01:03:17,840
克洛伊...
Chloe...

751
01:03:17,870 --> 01:03:19,800
我不行
No, I can't.

752
01:03:22,240 --> 01:03:24,110
我有一个小弟弟
You know, I have a younger brother,

753
01:03:24,140 --> 01:03:26,410
而且...
and, uh,

754
01:03:26,450 --> 01:03:31,180
他总有办法把我惹恼
he had this knack for just pissing me off.

755
01:03:31,220 --> 01:03:33,350
有一天他做得太过了
And one day he pushed it too far,

756
01:03:33,380 --> 01:03:36,650
于是不知怎的 我进入了他的脑中
and I somehow entered his mind.

757
01:03:36,690 --> 01:03:39,220
虽然不是故意的 可是我伤害了他
I hurt him. I didn't mean to,

758
01:03:39,260 --> 01:03:42,690
狠狠地伤害了他
but I hurt him badly.

759
01:03:42,730 --> 01:03:44,960
所以我逃走了
So I ran away.

760
01:04:03,850 --> 01:04:08,290
你的妻女 她们的名字是什么?
What were their names, your wife and daughter?

761
01:04:08,320 --> 01:04:10,260
我妻子叫海伦娜
Helena.

762
01:04:11,290 --> 01:04:13,320
女儿叫伊丽莎白
Elizabeth.

763
01:04:16,360 --> 01:04:19,860
我已经很久没有念过她们的名字了
I haven't said their names out loud in a long time.

764
01:04:24,870 --> 01:04:27,170
卡尔德 即使我想要帮助你
Kaulder, even if I wanted to help you,

765
01:04:27,210 --> 01:04:29,140
我也不知道从哪里入手
I wouldn't know where to begin.

766
01:04:32,080 --> 01:04:36,050
想一个可以关联起你我的词
Think of a word that you associate with me.

767
01:04:36,080 --> 01:04:38,720
什么都可以
Could be anything.

768
01:04:38,750 --> 01:04:41,950
把你的脑海放空
Empty everything else out of your head.

769
01:04:44,420 --> 01:04:47,360
把思想集中在那个词上面
And just focus on that one word.

770
01:04:47,390 --> 01:04:49,330
一个词
One word.

771
01:04:51,100 --> 01:04:53,900
告诉我那个词 我也会把思想集中在它上面
If you tell me the word, I'll focus on it, too.

772
01:04:53,930 --> 01:04:55,930
有时候这招会管用
Sometimes that helps.

773
01:04:55,970 --> 01:04:58,040
那个词是什么?
What's the word?

774
01:04:59,770 --> 01:05:01,770
孤独
Alone.

775
01:05:31,070 --> 01:05:33,200
抓住我的手
Take my hand.

776
01:06:09,610 --> 01:06:12,410
这边来 伙计们!
This way, men!

777
01:06:12,440 --> 01:06:14,550
多兰兄弟 看
Brother Dolan, look.

778
01:06:20,250 --> 01:06:21,990
卡尔德
Kaulder.

779
01:06:25,060 --> 01:06:27,560
那是什么? 多兰?
What is that? Dolan?

780
01:06:27,590 --> 01:06:30,060
小心点
Tread with care.

781
01:06:30,090 --> 01:06:32,230
他做到了
He did it.

782
01:06:35,370 --> 01:06:37,300
他成功杀死了黑巫后
So ends the Queen.

783
01:06:41,040 --> 01:06:42,610
以父之名...
In the name of the Father...

784
01:06:42,640 --> 01:06:44,410
他被附身了!
He's possessed!

785
01:06:44,440 --> 01:06:46,480
卡尔德还活着
Kaulder is alive.

786
01:06:46,510 --> 01:06:48,410
我们的噩梦在奇迹中结束
Our nightmare ends with a miracle.

787
01:06:48,450 --> 01:06:51,020
帮帮他
Help him.

788
01:06:51,050 --> 01:06:52,550
帮帮他
Help him.

789
01:06:55,620 --> 01:06:57,550
那是她的心脏
It's her heart.

790
01:06:57,590 --> 01:07:00,630
一旦我们摧毁了它 她就灰飞烟灭了
When we destroy it, we destroy her.

791
01:07:00,660 --> 01:07:02,590
你来摧毁它吧 多兰兄弟
End it, Brother Dolan.

792
01:07:23,380 --> 01:07:25,380
消灭她 多兰!
Destroy her, Dolan!

793
01:07:28,020 --> 01:07:29,950
不!
No!

794
01:07:36,060 --> 01:07:38,060
你竟然保留了它
You kept it.

795
01:07:39,300 --> 01:07:43,130
结束了 黑巫后死了
It's over. The Witch Queen is dead.

796
01:07:48,010 --> 01:07:50,570
他们从一开始就背叛了你
They betrayed you from the start.

797
01:07:50,610 --> 01:07:53,940
所以他们会折磨你的朋友
That's why they tortured your friend.

798
01:07:53,980 --> 01:07:56,410
因为他知道心脏的所在之处
Because he knew where the heart was.

799
01:07:56,450 --> 01:07:58,380
他们要复活黑巫后
They're gonna bring back the Queen.

800
01:08:06,360 --> 01:08:08,090
八百年了
For eight hundred years,

801
01:08:08,130 --> 01:08:09,860
我们一直在等待她的归来
we've waited for her return.

802
01:08:11,730 --> 01:08:13,560
你应该感到荣幸 叛徒
You should be honored, traitor.

803
01:08:13,600 --> 01:08:16,670
你将为我们的大业献出生命
You will be sacrificed for our cause.

804
01:08:20,570 --> 01:08:22,440
卡尔德 我知道贝利亚把那些土带去哪了
Kaulder, I know where Belial brought all that dirt.

805
01:08:22,470 --> 01:08:24,710
他租的那辆卡车有定位功...
The truck he rented had a standard GPS locator...

806
01:08:24,740 --> 01:08:26,280
你骗了我!
You lied to me!

807
01:08:26,310 --> 01:08:30,480
你保存着她的心脏 "回忆你的死亡"
You saved her heart. "Remember your death."

808
01:08:30,510 --> 01:08:32,480
不是你想的那样
It's not what you think.

809
01:08:34,720 --> 01:08:37,190
你一直知道这句话的意思 却什么也不说
You knew what it meant all along, and you said nothing.

810
01:08:37,220 --> 01:08:39,360
因为我不希望自己甫一上任
Because I wasn't going to be responsible

811
01:08:39,390 --> 01:08:42,030
就让十字斧教分崩离析...
for the dissolution of The Axe and Cross on my very first...

812
01:08:42,060 --> 01:08:44,160
他们要复活黑巫后
They're bringing back the Queen.

813
01:08:46,630 --> 01:08:48,670
你不知道自己干了什么
You don't know what you've done.

814
01:08:50,000 --> 01:08:53,140
我曾宣誓过要保守秘密
I swore an oath to keep it secret.

815
01:08:54,310 --> 01:08:58,610
数百年来 这秘密牵制着末日的降临
This lie has kept Apocalypse at bay for hundreds of years.

816
01:08:58,640 --> 01:09:01,110
我们害怕一旦黑巫后的心脏被毁
We were afraid if the Queen's heart was destroyed,

817
01:09:01,150 --> 01:09:03,210
你就会失去永生 甚至死亡
you'd lose your immortality. Or die.

818
01:09:03,250 --> 01:09:05,450
那不是由你们说了算!
That wasn't your choice to make!

819
01:09:09,050 --> 01:09:10,990
老多兰就是那么想的
That's what the old man thought.

820
01:09:13,460 --> 01:09:16,060
我想他被攻击的那晚
The night he was attacked,

821
01:09:16,090 --> 01:09:18,200
曾想要摧毁它
I think he was going to destroy it.

822
01:09:19,230 --> 01:09:21,170
为了你
For you.

823
01:09:26,740 --> 01:09:28,740
为了让你自由
To set you free.

824
01:09:39,050 --> 01:09:41,720
至少十字斧教还有他们的武器
At least The Axe and Cross still has their weapon.

825
01:09:48,130 --> 01:09:49,730
你将为黑巫后效命...
You will serve the Queen...

826
01:09:49,760 --> 01:09:51,760
不 拜托了
No, please.

827
01:09:51,800 --> 01:09:54,600
不管愿不愿意
like it or not.

828
01:10:21,460 --> 01:10:24,300
去我的公寓 那里很安全
Go to my apartment. You'll be safe there.

829
01:10:24,330 --> 01:10:27,130
不 说好了我们两一起行动的
No, the deal was that we stick together.

830
01:10:27,160 --> 01:10:28,770
我要一个人去 连自己人都不可信
I'm going alone. If I can't trust

831
01:10:28,800 --> 01:10:31,270
又凭什么相信你?
my own people, how the hell can I trust you?

832
01:10:33,840 --> 01:10:37,140
你不是这样的人
This isn't who you are.

833
01:10:37,170 --> 01:10:39,340
我就是这样的人
It's all I am.

834
01:11:09,610 --> 01:11:11,610
用铁刺她
Pierce her with iron.

835
01:11:11,640 --> 01:11:14,880
用火烧她
Scour her by fire.

836
01:11:14,910 --> 01:11:17,580
让她永远的死去
Bring her endless death.

837
01:11:44,840 --> 01:11:48,410
我很想念你 卡尔德
I've missed you, Kaulder.

838
01:11:48,410 --> 01:11:51,010
这就是你不明白的事
Here's what you don't understand.

839
01:11:51,040 --> 01:11:53,980
你的族人永远都不会明白的
What your kind never understood.

840
01:11:54,010 --> 01:11:56,550
我已经饶过你一次
I've shown mercy.

841
01:11:56,580 --> 01:11:59,980
我本可以把你们全部杀光的
I could have killed every last one of you.

842
01:12:00,020 --> 01:12:02,550
我计算过
I've done the math.

843
01:12:02,590 --> 01:12:04,590
我有过机会的
I've had the time.

844
01:12:04,620 --> 01:12:08,430
你现在和以前不同了 如此自信
You're different now. So confident.

845
01:12:08,460 --> 01:12:10,900
全靠你赐给我不死之身
Maybe you shouldn't have made me immortal.

846
01:12:13,330 --> 01:12:15,400
卡尔德 我是来帮忙的
Kaulder, I came to help.

847
01:12:15,430 --> 01:12:18,600
克洛伊 我告诉你不要...
Chloe. I told you not to...

848
01:12:49,330 --> 01:12:54,370
不死之身从来都不属于你 它是我的
Immortality was never yours. It was mine.

849
01:12:56,610 --> 01:12:59,170
你只是替我保管它
You just carried it for me.

850
01:12:59,510 --> 01:13:01,810
直到现在
Until now.

851
01:13:04,680 --> 01:13:08,320
我重生了
I am reborn.

852
01:13:39,220 --> 01:13:42,190
你的种族
Your race

853
01:13:42,220 --> 01:13:45,620
终日都在担惊受怕
has always been frightened.

854
01:13:48,560 --> 01:13:51,630
藏在洞穴里
Hiding in caves.

855
01:13:51,660 --> 01:13:54,170
挤在火堆旁
Huddling around fire.

856
01:13:56,070 --> 01:13:57,370
终于
Finally.

857
01:15:02,330 --> 01:15:05,770
嘿 孩子 我还在担心是不是太晚了
Hey, kid. I was afraid I was too late.

858
01:15:05,800 --> 01:15:08,710
但愿我的样子没你那么糟
I hope I don't look as rough as you do.

859
01:15:09,740 --> 01:15:12,410
好了
Okay.

860
01:15:15,380 --> 01:15:17,380
我杀死了诅咒你的人
I killed the one who cursed you.

861
01:15:17,420 --> 01:15:19,850
来
Here.

862
01:15:19,880 --> 01:15:21,820
把这个喝了
Drink this.

863
01:15:27,360 --> 01:15:29,290
谢谢
Thank you.

864
01:15:31,830 --> 01:15:34,300
黑巫后复活了
The Witch Queen has returned.

865
01:15:35,600 --> 01:15:37,400
我以为我的不死之身
I thought my immortality

866
01:15:37,430 --> 01:15:39,900
是她惩罚我的方法
was the way that she punished me.

867
01:15:39,940 --> 01:15:43,740
但她只是利用我来为她保存生机
But she just used me to save it for herself.

868
01:15:43,770 --> 01:15:46,780
我恐怕也难逃其咎
I'm afraid I bear some responsibility.

869
01:15:46,810 --> 01:15:48,850
我们太狂妄自大了
It was hubris to think

870
01:15:48,880 --> 01:15:52,350
竟以为敌人发现不了我们的秘密
that our secret wouldn't be discovered by the enemy.

871
01:15:52,380 --> 01:15:55,350
我预见到接下来会发生什么
I've seen what comes next.

872
01:15:55,390 --> 01:15:57,460
死亡
Death.

873
01:15:58,960 --> 01:16:02,860
黑巫后会散播新的瘟疫诅咒
The Witch Queen will cast another plague curse.

874
01:16:02,890 --> 01:16:06,830
能散播瘟疫的巫师竟没有被摧毁吗?
Haven't covens with that kind of power been destroyed?

875
01:16:06,870 --> 01:16:08,930
如今我们不摧毁巫师了
We don't destroy witches anymore.

876
01:16:08,970 --> 01:16:11,670
我们囚禁他们
We incarcerate them.

877
01:16:14,310 --> 01:16:16,410
我们把世界上
We took all the most powerful witches

878
01:16:16,440 --> 01:16:17,480
最厉害的巫师们抓起来
that ever walked the Earth

879
01:16:17,510 --> 01:16:19,680
并把他们放在一个地方
and put 'em in one place.

880
01:16:19,710 --> 01:16:21,950
巫师监狱
The witch prison.

881
01:16:21,980 --> 01:16:26,450
他们一直等待着被释放
And they've been waiting, waiting to be released.

882
01:16:26,480 --> 01:16:28,820
等待着复仇
Waiting to exact revenge.

883
01:16:31,590 --> 01:16:33,930
我们创造了完美的巫师团
We created the perfect coven.

884
01:16:35,860 --> 01:16:39,830
现在我又回到了原点
Now I'm right back where I started.

885
01:16:41,800 --> 01:16:44,830
你打败过她一次
You defeated her once.

886
01:16:44,870 --> 01:16:47,770
你一定能再次打败她
You can defeat her again.

887
01:16:47,810 --> 01:16:49,740
卡尔德
Kaulder,

888
01:16:50,940 --> 01:16:52,880
你必须去
you must go.

889
01:16:54,650 --> 01:16:56,610
你必须战斗
You have to fight.

890
01:17:13,470 --> 01:17:15,400
卡尔德
Kaulder.

891
01:17:20,740 --> 01:17:22,870
我从未给它起过名字
I never had a name for it.

892
01:17:24,810 --> 01:17:27,610
但我的敌人管它叫"海克森贝因"
But my enemies came to call it "Hexenbane."

893
01:17:29,050 --> 01:17:31,410
斩巫剑
Witch Slayer.

894
01:17:31,450 --> 01:17:33,250
我也要去
I'm coming, too.

895
01:17:33,290 --> 01:17:35,850
我们的协约是我保证你的安全
Our agreement depended on me keeping you safe.

896
01:17:35,890 --> 01:17:37,690
不 我们的协约是如果我帮助你
No, our agreement was that if I helped you,

897
01:17:37,720 --> 01:17:39,620
你保证我的安全
you'd keep me safe.

898
01:17:39,660 --> 01:17:41,890
如果我现在受伤 它不会自愈的
If I get hurt now, I stay hurt.

899
01:17:41,930 --> 01:17:44,860
你要怎么办?
Where would that leave you?

900
01:17:44,900 --> 01:17:47,400
我才不在乎呢!
You know, I don't care!

901
01:17:47,430 --> 01:17:49,630
谁说巫师不能追杀巫师了?
Who says that a witch can't hunt witches?

902
01:18:06,650 --> 01:18:08,590
克洛伊
Chloe.

903
01:18:09,790 --> 01:18:11,860
卡尔德
Kaulder.

904
01:18:25,570 --> 01:18:27,470
这是什么?
What is this?

905
01:18:27,510 --> 01:18:29,540
瘟疫之树 她就在这里
It's a plague tree. She's here.

906
01:18:29,570 --> 01:18:30,980
咒语完成后
When the spell is done,

907
01:18:31,010 --> 01:18:33,640
蝇群就会被释放
the fly swarm will be released.

908
01:18:33,680 --> 01:18:35,850
我们时间不多了
We haven't much time.

909
01:18:46,690 --> 01:18:48,630
跟紧了
Stay close.

910
01:18:55,900 --> 01:18:58,540
卡尔德 囚犯们都去哪了?
Kaulder, where are the prisoners?

911
01:19:06,580 --> 01:19:08,510
天啊!
My God!

912
01:19:10,980 --> 01:19:13,120
我抓获的每一个巫师
Every witch I ever caught.

913
01:19:13,150 --> 01:19:15,720
都被黑巫后当做了释放瘟疫的力量之源
The Queen's using their power to release the plague.

914
01:19:15,750 --> 01:19:17,360
怎么做到的?
How?

915
01:19:17,390 --> 01:19:19,090
咒颂
The chant.

916
01:19:19,120 --> 01:19:20,520
没有巫师能强大到
No witch would be strong enough

917
01:19:20,560 --> 01:19:21,790
独自承担这个咒语的作用
to cast this spell alone.

918
01:19:21,830 --> 01:19:23,430
但黑巫后把他们的思想
But the Witch Queen's

919
01:19:23,460 --> 01:19:25,100
像链条一样连接起来了
linking their minds like a chain.

920
01:19:25,130 --> 01:19:27,070
我们该如何阻止他们?
So how do we stop them?

921
01:19:28,570 --> 01:19:30,730
每个链条都有弱点
Every chain has a weak link.

922
01:20:03,840 --> 01:20:05,870
- 我来杀死他 - 不要
- I'll do the honors. - No.

923
01:20:05,900 --> 01:20:07,770
我们需要消灭的不是他的肉体
It's not his body we need to destroy.

924
01:20:07,810 --> 01:20:09,840
是他的思想
It's his mind.

925
01:20:11,680 --> 01:20:13,080
但如果他死在了梦中
But if he dies in his dreams,

926
01:20:13,110 --> 01:20:15,010
瘟疫就能被阻止
the plague will be stopped.

927
01:20:15,050 --> 01:20:17,120
我希望还有别的办法
I wish there was another way.

928
01:20:20,650 --> 01:20:22,920
当我回来后你还会在这里 是吧?
You'll still be here when I get back, right?

929
01:20:25,520 --> 01:20:28,730
你要和黑巫后单挑 是吗?
You're taking on the Queen alone, aren't you?

930
01:20:28,760 --> 01:20:30,890
这必须有个了结
It has to end.

931
01:20:36,800 --> 01:20:39,470
嘿
Hey.

932
01:20:39,500 --> 01:20:41,240
在里面注意安全
Be careful in there.

933
01:20:42,840 --> 01:20:45,810
你现在又开始关心我了啊?
So are you worried about me then?

934
01:20:45,840 --> 01:20:48,550
我已经习惯你了
Well, I've gotten used to you.

935
01:20:51,150 --> 01:20:52,750
追杀愉快
Good hunting.

936
01:20:52,780 --> 01:20:54,890
你也是
You, too.

937
01:21:26,680 --> 01:21:28,020
守卫
The Sentinel.

938
01:21:28,050 --> 01:21:29,890
不把囚犯关进牢里
And it won't stop until this prisoner

939
01:21:29,920 --> 01:21:33,020
它是不会停的
is put back in his cell.

940
01:21:39,760 --> 01:21:42,200
它是冲着埃里克来的
It's coming for Ellic.

941
01:22:15,270 --> 01:22:17,270
卡尔德?
Kaulder?

942
01:23:35,410 --> 01:23:37,110
如果她出现了受伤的迹象
If there's any sign she's getting hurt in there,

943
01:23:37,150 --> 01:23:38,180
你必须要把她唤醒
you have to wake her up.

944
01:23:38,220 --> 01:23:40,780
向我保证你会把她带到别处
And promise me you'll get her as far away

945
01:23:40,820 --> 01:23:41,880
越远越好
from here as you can.

946
01:23:41,920 --> 01:23:43,250
没问题
Of course.

947
01:24:51,350 --> 01:24:52,660
咒颂停止了
The chanting stopped.

948
01:24:55,460 --> 01:24:57,590
她成功了
She did it.

949
01:25:50,410 --> 01:25:53,750
一个梦行者能为你展示过去
A dream-walker shows your past.

950
01:25:53,780 --> 01:25:56,650
但只有我能向你展示未来
Only I can show the future.

951
01:25:57,950 --> 01:26:01,760
你会失败 人类将要灭绝
You will fail, and humanity will fall.

952
01:26:08,800 --> 01:26:10,570
我已经统治世界了
I've taken this world back.

953
01:26:10,600 --> 01:26:12,540
还没有
Not yet.

954
01:26:17,910 --> 01:26:19,910
你能感觉到吗?
Can you feel it?

955
01:26:19,940 --> 01:26:22,610
你的肉体凡胎?
Your mortality?

956
01:26:22,650 --> 01:26:26,220
你的生命正在流逝?
Your life ebbing away?

957
01:27:03,020 --> 01:27:04,960
爸爸!
Father!

958
01:27:09,430 --> 01:27:10,890
卡尔德
Kaulder.

959
01:27:17,030 --> 01:27:19,400
你们是我们世界的入侵者
You are trespassers on our world.

960
01:27:19,440 --> 01:27:21,440
爸爸!
Father!

961
01:27:21,470 --> 01:27:23,310
我从你眼中就能看出来
I've seen it in your eyes.

962
01:27:23,340 --> 01:27:26,410
你渴望死亡
You wish for death.

963
01:27:58,340 --> 01:28:01,480
你知道永生的好处是什么吗?
You know the benefit of eternal life?

964
01:28:01,510 --> 01:28:03,480
就是我能杀死你两次
I get to kill you twice.

965
01:28:04,950 --> 01:28:06,450
住手!
Stop!

966
01:28:06,480 --> 01:28:08,650
卡尔德!
Kaulder!

967
01:28:08,690 --> 01:28:09,990
现在...
Now...

968
01:28:10,020 --> 01:28:11,320
- 克洛伊... - 很抱歉
- Chloe... - I'm sorry.

969
01:28:11,360 --> 01:28:14,060
放走我的皇后
Release my Queen.

970
01:28:14,090 --> 01:28:16,560
在我小时候 你从巫师手中救出了我...
Those witches you rescued me from when I was a kid...

971
01:28:16,590 --> 01:28:19,730
他们没有杀死我父母 他们就是我父母
They didn't kill my parents. They were my parents.

972
01:28:19,760 --> 01:28:21,360
不幸的是 我生来就没有魔法
But sadly, I was born without magic.

973
01:28:21,400 --> 01:28:22,370
你是个巫师
You're a witch.

974
01:28:22,400 --> 01:28:24,330
对
Yep.

975
01:28:25,970 --> 01:28:28,500
- 不要! 不要! - 回来!
- No! No! - Get back here!

976
01:28:30,410 --> 01:28:32,580
离他远点! 放开我!
Get away from him! Let go!

977
01:28:45,490 --> 01:28:47,420
梦行者
Dream-walker.

978
01:29:43,810 --> 01:29:45,450
看看你
Look at you,

979
01:29:45,480 --> 01:29:48,950
真是个肮脏的早晨
you ugly bitch of a morning.

980
01:30:00,660 --> 01:30:02,470
你最后背叛了
You turned against those

981
01:30:02,500 --> 01:30:04,000
你被要求保护的人
you were charged with protecting.

982
01:30:04,030 --> 01:30:05,900
是的 女王陛下
Yes, my Queen.

983
01:30:05,940 --> 01:30:09,070
使我完整 祝我成功
Make me whole. Help me reach my destiny.

984
01:30:09,110 --> 01:30:11,540
赐予我魔法吧
Grant me the gift of magic.

985
01:30:11,570 --> 01:30:14,040
陶土不可能变成黄金
Clay cannot be turned to gold.

986
01:30:14,080 --> 01:30:17,910
没有魔法 你就是一个凡人
Without magic, you're just a human.

987
01:30:45,640 --> 01:30:47,580
父亲?
Father?

988
01:30:52,680 --> 01:30:54,720
亲爱的
My love.

989
01:30:58,250 --> 01:31:00,590
你必须站起来
You must get up.

990
01:31:03,190 --> 01:31:05,800
父亲 你得站起来
Father, you need to get up.

991
01:31:06,830 --> 01:31:08,960
拯救他们
Save them.

992
01:31:15,610 --> 01:31:19,110
去吧 我的爱人 战斗吧
Go, my love. Fight.

993
01:32:00,250 --> 01:32:02,920
你不肯放弃自己可悲的人生
You cling to your pathetic life.

994
01:32:02,950 --> 01:32:04,920
为的是什么?
And for what reason?

995
01:32:06,260 --> 01:32:09,020
最亲近你的人背叛了你
Those closest to you betray you,

996
01:32:09,060 --> 01:32:12,760
你宣称要保护的人们根本不知道你的名字
and those you claim to protect don't even know your name.

997
01:32:15,670 --> 01:32:17,670
以铁
By iron

998
01:32:19,340 --> 01:32:21,570
和火焰之名
and fire!

999
01:33:22,230 --> 01:33:25,900
你倒是用iPad拍死它试试
Try doing that with an iPad.

1000
01:33:38,880 --> 01:33:41,350
卡尔德!
Kaulder!

1001
01:33:41,380 --> 01:33:43,320
卡尔德?
Kaulder?

1002
01:33:48,730 --> 01:33:50,790
卡尔德?
Kaulder?

1003
01:34:27,230 --> 01:34:29,830
只要黑巫后的心脏还在跳动
As long as the Hexen heart beats,

1004
01:34:29,870 --> 01:34:32,300
她就永远不会真正死去
she's never truly dead.

1005
01:34:33,940 --> 01:34:36,340
不 你不能! 你会死的
No, you can't! You'll die.

1006
01:34:37,770 --> 01:34:39,240
我已经准备好接受现实了
I'm ready to face that reality.

1007
01:34:39,280 --> 01:34:42,140
不行! 一定还有别的方法
No! There must be another way.

1008
01:34:42,180 --> 01:34:44,910
听我说
Listen to me.

1009
01:34:44,950 --> 01:34:47,080
当我被拉进阴影时
When I was pulled into the shadows,

1010
01:34:47,120 --> 01:34:50,450
我看到了比她还糟糕的东西
I saw that there were things much worse than her.

1011
01:34:50,490 --> 01:34:53,990
她们在黑暗中 等待着
In the darkness. Waiting.

1012
01:34:54,020 --> 01:34:56,290
等什么?
Waiting for what?

1013
01:34:56,330 --> 01:34:58,290
一个没有你的世界
The world without you.

1014
01:34:59,500 --> 01:35:02,800
我们还需要你
We still need you.

1015
01:35:02,830 --> 01:35:05,170
我需要你
I need you.

1016
01:35:09,270 --> 01:35:12,110
十字斧教背叛了我
The Axe and Cross betrayed me.

1017
01:35:12,140 --> 01:35:13,480
我谁都不能相信
I can't trust anyone.

1018
01:35:13,510 --> 01:35:15,710
你可以相信我
You can trust me.

1019
01:35:18,320 --> 01:35:21,180
这条路我走了800年
800 years I've been on this road.

1020
01:35:26,090 --> 01:35:29,290
终日追杀
Always hunting.

1021
01:35:29,330 --> 01:35:32,390
- 终日... - 独身一人
- Always... - Alone.

1022
01:35:32,430 --> 01:35:34,900
你不会的
You wouldn't be.

1023
01:35:41,440 --> 01:35:44,010
另外
Besides,

1024
01:35:44,040 --> 01:35:47,310
你还欠我五万块钱呢
you still owe me fifty thousand dollars.

1025
01:35:48,480 --> 01:35:50,010
是五千块
Five thousand.

1026
01:35:50,050 --> 01:35:53,180
噢 想讨价还价哈?
Oh. So we're negotiating, then?

1027
01:36:01,420 --> 01:36:03,490
十字斧教会因为黑巫后的心脏
The Axe and Cross would be bothered that

1028
01:36:03,530 --> 01:36:04,760
不再受他们掌控
they're no longer in possession

1029
01:36:04,790 --> 01:36:06,330
而十分烦恼的
of the Queen's heart.

1030
01:36:06,360 --> 01:36:09,200
我以后不为十字斧教效命了
I don't serve The Axe and Cross anymore.

1031
01:36:09,230 --> 01:36:11,200
这次我是为自己活着
This time I do it for me.

1032
01:36:11,230 --> 01:36:13,170
嗯 是时候了
Well, it's about time.

1033
01:36:16,210 --> 01:36:17,470
你知道吗 我曾经觉得
You know, I used to think

1034
01:36:17,510 --> 01:36:20,080
宇宙万物只是无休止的轮回
the universe ran in endless circles,

1035
01:36:20,110 --> 01:36:23,280
永远都在重复自己 永远不出预料
always repeating itself, always predictable.

1036
01:36:24,850 --> 01:36:26,780
现在呢?
And now?

1037
01:36:28,580 --> 01:36:31,990
我不知道下一步会发生什么
I don't know what happens next.

1038
01:36:32,020 --> 01:36:35,260
你知道我们凡人管它叫什么吗?
Do you know what we mortals call that?

1039
01:36:35,290 --> 01:36:37,290
生活
Living.

1040
01:36:42,500 --> 01:36:45,070
知道吗
You know,

1041
01:36:45,100 --> 01:36:48,040
我还是需要你
I still need you.

1042
01:36:48,070 --> 01:36:50,270
那好
Well, then

1043
01:36:50,310 --> 01:36:52,480
愿意为您服务
I'm at your service.

1044
01:36:54,910 --> 01:36:57,450
来吧 你又不会变年轻
Come on. You're not getting any younger.

1045
01:37:01,080 --> 01:37:03,320
所以你准备好出发了还是怎么?
So you ready to go, or what?

1046
01:37:05,060 --> 01:37:06,990
我开车
I'm driving.

1047
01:37:10,290 --> 01:37:12,460
好
Okay.

